<paragraph id="522636F3FFF8FF88FF4661EAFDEBFA5F" blockId="9.[178,1086,1416,1486]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1226">
M a t e r i a l e x a m i n e d: 
<collectingCountry id="2A8E7663FFF8FF88FE1D61EAFDC8FA0F" box="[489,553,1416,1438]" name="China" pageId="9" pageNumber="1226">China</collectingCountry>
: 13, N-Sichuan, 
<quantity id="95619B16FFF8FF88FD3161EAFD1EFA0F" box="[709,767,1416,1438]" metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="1226" unit="km" value="70.0">70 km</quantity>
N Songpan, road S 301, above Gan lake, 
<geoCoordinate id="37AD5034FFF8FF88FEE661C2FEBAFA27" box="[274,347,1440,1462]" degrees="33" direction="north" minutes="15" orientation="latitude" pageId="9" pageNumber="1226" precision="925" value="33.25">33°15'N</geoCoordinate>
